window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Reality Check.</b></p> <p>After rescuing Amy and dismantling the twisted experimentation lab, Xay and his team get honored as heroes.</p> <p>However, Cosmos Academy responds with brutal, individualized coaching—forcing them to confront their weaknesses and face the true scale of power within the Awakened World.</p> <p>They each train hard to master their abilities before their second awakening, but Xay takes on two extra challenges along the way: psychic force—and earning the approval of Kimi’s intense family.</p>"; 
